I absolutely hate that weak look,
form and cry!

54
00:03:30,443 --> 00:03:32,312
It drains the strength from me.

55
00:03:32,312 --> 00:03:33,813
How exaggerated.

56
00:03:33,813 --> 00:03:37,083
As a sweeper, you have a fearsome
reputation in the underworld.

57
00:03:37,083 --> 00:03:40,177
You'll become a laughingstock if they
ever learn that you fear cats.

58
00:03:41,387 --> 00:03:45,024
They can laugh all they want.
Cats are my natural enemy.

59
00:03:45,024 --> 00:03:46,924
Oh, you're not a mouse, you know.

60
00:03:48,995 --> 00:03:52,658
It's here! Go away! Please, do something!

61
00:04:01,507 --> 00:04:03,309
I can't believe Falcon!

62
